"""
PART III Income

15. Income for the purposes of the Act

(1)

Editorial note: current text valid from 2025-03-21.

For the purposes of section 15(1)(e) (income), all social security benefits are prescribed except—

(aa)

personal independence payment;
"""

relevant_benefit_is_social_security_benefit:
    entity: Person
    period: Day
    dtype: Boolean

relevant_benefit_is_personal_independence_payment:
    entity: Person
    period: Day
    dtype: Boolean

personal_independence_payment_is_excepted_from_prescribed_social_security_benefits_15_1_aa:
    entity: Person
    period: Day
    dtype: Boolean
    from 2025-03-21:
        if relevant_benefit_is_social_security_benefit: relevant_benefit_is_personal_independence_payment else: false
